        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="legend-note" parent="legend-box" style="text;html=1;fontSize=10;fontColor=#666666;align=left;" value="&lt;i&gt;Domain Services are external consumers of the&lt;br&gt;platform. OPA is a shared policy engine used by&lt;br&gt;both ForgeRock (auth-level) and Domain Services&lt;br&gt;(domain-level), with profile context from the platform.&lt;/i&gt;" vertex="1">
